<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 06:08:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在周一的日全食期间见证“行星游行”等</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/witness-planetary-parade-among-other-things-during-mondays-total-solar-eclipse/articleshow/109101306.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109101306.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 4 月 8 日，日食将使世界某些地区变暗，为沿途的人们提供罕见的白天黑暗和日冕景象。观测者将欣赏到一场独特的“行星游行”，七颗行星——天王星、木星、水星、金星、海王星、土星和火星——在全食期间出现在太阳附近。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 05:48:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/witness-planetary-parade-among-other-things-during-mondays-total-solar-eclipse/articleshow/109101306.cms</guid></item><item><title>卢旺达回顾种族灭绝 30 周年</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/rwanda-commemorates-30-years-since-genocide/articleshow/109101164.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109101164.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;卢旺达人将于周日纪念胡图族极端分子策划的种族灭绝导致国家分裂30周年，邻国之间互相残杀，这是20世纪最血腥的屠杀之一。每年全国各地都会发现新的乱葬坑。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 05:36:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/rwanda-commemorates-30-years-since-genocide/articleshow/109101164.cms</guid></item><item><title>一些与建制派有联系的 PTI 领导人：伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan)</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/some-pti-leaders-in-touch-with-establishment-imran-khan/articleshow/109099934.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099934.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 5 月 9 日爆发暴力事件后，巴基斯坦正义运动 (PTI) 面临逮捕和开小差等压力，伊姆兰·汗周六表示，该党的一些领导人仍与该组织保持联系。黎明报道。卡迪尔信托案听证会结束后，汗表示，为了巴基斯坦，他愿意与任何人举行会谈。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 04:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/some-pti-leaders-in-touch-with-establishment-imran-khan/articleshow/109099934.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国在有争议的南海进行军事演习</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-conducts-military-exercises-in-contested-south-china-sea/articleshow/109100590.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109100590.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国军队在南海进行了“战斗巡逻”，同时菲律宾、美国、日本和澳大利亚举行了联合演习。解放军宣布“海空联合巡逻”以控制紧张局势。美国重申保护菲律宾的承诺，引发中方不满。该地区地缘政治紧张局势加剧，领土主张相互竞争，共同努力维持稳定。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 04:50:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-conducts-military-exercises-in-contested-south-china-sea/articleshow/109100590.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦部长可能访问中国平息炸弹爆炸影响</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-minister-likely-to-visit-china-to-quell-bomb-blast-after-effects/articleshow/109099983.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099983.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;近期开伯尔-普赫图赫瓦省发生恐怖袭击事件，导致 5 名中国工程师丧生，巴基斯坦外交部长伊沙克·达尔 (Ishaq Dar) 计划访问中国，以应对中国企业的安全担忧。这次袭击不仅使该项目陷入停滞，还引发了国际企业对该地区员工安全的担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 05:04:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-minister-likely-to-visit-china-to-quell-bomb-blast-after-effects/articleshow/109099983.cms</guid></item><item><title>新西兰对就业签证计划进行修改以管理净移民</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/new-zealand-implements-changes-to-employment-visa-program-to-manage-net-migration/articleshow/109100506.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109100506.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新西兰政府对其就业签证计划进行了修改，旨在解决“不可持续”的净移民问题。这些改变包括英语语言要求和减少低技能职位的停留时间。此举是出于对创纪录的移民水平的担忧，可能会影响住房需求。尽管劳动年龄人口增长放缓，央行仍对通胀压力持谨慎态度。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 04:47:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/new-zealand-implements-changes-to-employment-visa-program-to-manage-net-migration/articleshow/109100506.cms</guid></item><item><title>新西兰航空一名乘客在飞行途中在杯子里小便，面临罚款和指控</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/air-new-zealand-passenger-faces-fines-and-charges-after-urinating-in-cup-mid-flight/articleshow/109100020.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109100020.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新西兰航空一架从奥克兰飞往悉尼机场的航班上，一名乘客因在延误下机期间在杯子里小便而面临罚款和指控。据《Stuff》报道，该事件涉及该男子在其他乘客旁边的杯子里小便，造成不适和混乱。他因影响安全的攻击行为被罚款600澳元。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 04:18:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/air-new-zealand-passenger-faces-fines-and-charges-after-urinating-in-cup-mid-flight/articleshow/109100020.cms</guid></item><item><title>2024 年美国总统大选：唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 从迄今为止规模最大的筹款活动中筹集了 5000 万美元</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-presidential-election-2024-donald-trump-raises-50-million-from-largest-fundraiser-yet/articleshow/109100037.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109100037.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 04:08:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-presidential-election-2024-donald-trump-raises-50-million-from-largest-fundraiser-yet/articleshow/109100037.cms</guid></item><item><title>耶伦表示，美国和中国需要“艰难”的对话</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/us-china-need-tough-conversations-yellen-tells/articleshow/109099837.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099837.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦在与中国总理李强会面时强调了进行艰难讨论的重要性。李克强也强调了两国之间相互尊重和伙伴关系的必要性。耶伦强调管理华盛顿和北京之间错综复杂的关系的共同责任，特别是解决了对中国工厂产能过剩的担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/us-china-need-tough-conversations-yellen-tells/articleshow/109099837.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本将加入 Aukus 的扩张计划以威慑中国：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/japan-to-join-aukus-in-expected-expansion-to-deter-china-report/articleshow/109099140.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099140.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国、英国和澳大利亚将扩大奥库斯协议，将日本纳入其对华威慑战略的一部分。消息人士证实，奥库斯国防部长将宣布就该协议的“第二支柱”进行会谈，重点是量子计算、海底技术、高超音速、人工智能和网络能力方面的联合开发。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:39:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/japan-to-join-aukus-in-expected-expansion-to-deter-china-report/articleshow/109099140.cms</guid></item><item><title>尽管遭遇挫折，美国核工业仍对小型反应堆持乐观态度</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-nuclear-industry-upbeat-on-small-reactors-despite-setback/articleshow/109099571.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099571.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尽管 NuScale 在美国核项目中遭遇挫折，但无碳电力项目的希望依然存在。积极的前景包括 GE Hitachi 设计的 BWRX-300 和田纳西河谷管理局的投资。努力的目标是标准化和降低成本。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:22:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-nuclear-industry-upbeat-on-small-reactors-despite-setback/articleshow/109099571.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦正义运动党提名阿里·扎法尔为参议院反对党领袖候选人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-tehreek-e-insaf-nominates-ali-zafar-as-candidate-for-opposition-leader-in-senate/articleshow/109099560.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099560.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:21:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-tehreek-e-insaf-nominates-ali-zafar-as-candidate-for-opposition-leader-in-senate/articleshow/109099560.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国派遣皇家海军舰艇加强对加沙的援助并建立新的海上走廊</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-sends-royal-navy-ship-to-boost-aid-for-gaza-and-set-up-a-new-maritime-corridor/articleshow/109099186.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099186.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 02:47:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-sends-royal-navy-ship-to-boost-aid-for-gaza-and-set-up-a-new-maritime-corridor/articleshow/109099186.cms</guid></item><item><title>载有南卡罗来纳大学兄弟会的巴士在密西西比州发生翻车事故 11人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/11-injured-as-bus-carrying-university-of-south-carolina-fraternity-crashes-in-mississippi/articleshow/109098641.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109098641.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;密西西比州圣路易斯湾附近发生一起涉及南卡罗来纳大学学生的巴士事故，造成 11 人受伤。司机蒂娜·威尔逊和一名学生受重伤，其他人被送往医院。威尔逊的敏捷思维和学生保罗·克鲁恩的干预避免了一场潜在的灾难。该大学正在为受影响的学生提供支持。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 01:31:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/11-injured-as-bus-carrying-university-of-south-carolina-fraternity-crashes-in-mississippi/articleshow/109098641.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列空袭黎巴嫩真主党训练营</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-conducts-air-strikes-on-hezbollah-training-camp-in-lebanon/articleshow/109098367.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109098367.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列对黎巴嫩东部贝卡谷地的一个真主党训练营进行了空袭。真主党击落一架以色列无人机后，紧张局势升级。巴勒贝克附近的萨弗里镇遭到袭击，没有人员伤亡报告。真主党证实了无人机被击落的消息，并强调了持续的敌对行动。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 00:48:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-conducts-air-strikes-on-hezbollah-training-camp-in-lebanon/articleshow/109098367.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿富汗发生4.3级地震</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/earthquake-of-magnitude-4-3-strikes-afghanistan/articleshow/109098039.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109098039.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 00:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/earthquake-of-magnitude-4-3-strikes-afghanistan/articleshow/109098039.cms</guid></item><item><title>“继续支持以色列”：苏纳克表示以色列与哈马斯的冲突“必须结束”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/continue-to-stand-by-israel-sunak-says-israel-hamas-conflict-must-end/articleshow/109097369.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109097369.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相里希·苏纳克支持以色列与哈马斯的冲突，呼吁结束暴力并释放人质。敦促加沙人道主义暂停，提及伤亡情况，并强调英国公众情绪。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 23:30:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/continue-to-stand-by-israel-sunak-says-israel-hamas-conflict-must-end/articleshow/109097369.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国难民署呼吁提供 6.2 亿美元支持伊朗和巴基斯坦的阿富汗移民</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/unhcr-appeals-for-usd-620-million-to-support-afghan-migrants-in-iran-and-pakistan/articleshow/109097042.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109097042.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国难民署呼吁提供 6.2 亿美元援助伊朗和巴基斯坦境内的阿富汗移民，以应对阿富汗的严峻形势。该报告预计到 2024 年将向 480 万阿富汗移民和 250 万收容社区成员提供援助，并强调迫切需要人道主义援助来帮助 2,370 万人生存。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 23:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/unhcr-appeals-for-usd-620-million-to-support-afghan-migrants-in-iran-and-pakistan/articleshow/109097042.cms</guid></item><item><title>彼得·佩莱格里尼赢得斯洛伐克总统选举</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/peter-pellegrini-wins-slovakia-presidential-elections/articleshow/109096954.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109096954.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在斯洛伐克，彼得·佩莱格里尼 (Peter Pellegrini) 以 53% 的支持率击败伊万·科尔科克 (Ivan Korcok) 的 47% 赢得总统选举。科尔科克优雅地认输，强调对结果的尊重。这次选举的焦点是对乌克兰冲突的不同看法，佩莱格里尼主张和谈。这场胜利反映了斯洛伐克在战争和外交上的立场。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 23:05:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/peter-pellegrini-wins-slovakia-presidential-elections/articleshow/109096954.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国对阿富汗妇女和儿童营养不良激增发出警告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/un-raises-alarm-on-surging-malnutrition-in-afghan-women-and-children/articleshow/109096386.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109096386.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国世界粮食计划署驻阿富汗办事处对妇女和儿童营养不良率不断上升表示担忧，喀布尔的营养不良病例在三年内增加了两倍。人道主义援助的减少加剧了这一问题，影响了营养不良患者的心理健康和设施。贫困、不安全和塔利班的限制使局势进一步恶化。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 22:39:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/un-raises-alarm-on-surging-malnutrition-in-afghan-women-and-children/articleshow/109096386.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>